  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Clean Water for 200 Displaced Syrian Families</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Seven years of war and violence has forced nearly 12 million Syrians from their homes, fleeing for their lives. As a result, Syrians lack sufficient access to water, sanitation and health care services. GlobalMedic will deliver 200 Family Emergency Kits for 1,200 people. Each kit includes one Rainfresh Household Water Purification Unit and one Hygiene Kit to support the health of families displaced by the conflict in Syria. Each kit purchased will be matched 1 to 1 by a GlobalMedic donor.</narrative>
  </description>
